subproject.corporate outcome: Capacities of national and local institutions enhanced to scale up proven MDG acceleration interventions and to plan, monitor, report and evaluate the MDG progress in the context of related national development priorities
subproject.description: The initiative seeks to assist the government in developing an overall national strategic framework to address the HIV/AISD epidemic. It comprises of the development of three strategic documents - draft National Strategy on HIV and AIDS, draft National Action Plan and draft National Monitoring and Evaluation Framework. All 3 documents will then be presented to the government for consideration to be adopted as the National Strategy for HIV and AIDS for the duration of 2011 – 2015.
subproject.title: SEDC: HIV NSP 2011-2015
